Package org.eclipse.collections.api.set

Interface MultiReaderSet<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Collection<T>, InternalIterable<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>, MutableCollection<T>, MutableSet<T>, MutableSetIterable<T>, RichIterable<T>, java.util.Set<T>, SetIterable<T>, UnsortedSetIterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiReaderUnifiedSet
    public interface MultiReaderSet<T>
extends MutableSet<T>
    A MultiReaderSet provides thread-safe iteration for a set through methods withReadLockAndDelegate() and withWriteLockAndDelegate().
    Since:
    10.0.
